Interface AvesObject

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvesObjectImpl

    public interface AvesObject
    Interface defining the type of the objects presented in Aves JOURNEYS. Classes implementing this interface can be be rendered in a DataViewer.
    Author:
    svlieffe 2012/03/29
